data.description: Come check out this great opportunity for single-level living in Trinity! This wonderful manufactured home has plenty of space, a flat lot, and tons of potential! While the home needs a little TLC, that doesn't mean it isnt great. You wont see this level of listing price in Trinity often, so take advantage of it now!
